          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/7581796-the-lightning-thief">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1487274943" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13016484858231376604">I found a file on my computer with pictures of percabeth fanarts and felt the urge to re-read this masterpiece.<br/>Read it in one breath. YES YES YES. I miss all of these characters 🖤</span>

          </span>
